01:21:05,718 --> 01:21:22,525
We know that this is still going to be tight staffing. If you look at the first 15 minutes, 15, 20 minutes of the day, you can really see that there's only one space available. And that is, and then the outside there, it's the cafeteria for snack and meeting.

