01:27:05,341 --> 01:27:31,497
this is a problem in almost every district. So this is not an issue that Medford is facing alone. It's been really wonderful for us to be able to do some work in trying to make that not a major issue for parents because it is something that every community is really struggling to deal with and is going to need to figure out a solution for. So thank you again for inviting us to be part of this process with all of you.

