there are wait lists again. So it can't be your one solution. So it's a yes and. Yeah, so it's a yes and. But I would say, I would recommend, it depends on the, the vouchers come from the state and then they're sent to these different programs, these different organizations that facilitate the vouchers through a voucher counselor who works individually with the family. So you're a little bit at the,

355
02:25:36,877 --> 02:25:54,224
I'm not going to get into that. I'm not going to get into that. I'm not going to get into that.

