398
02:42:33,325 --> 02:42:52,597
A child, a five-year-old child, needs to have their needs met in the program. And that might also mean that you need to play some sort of, it's not a management role, but you need to be able to facilitate a group of, a team of teachers in that space, if you have a very large group, to have station play happening.

